{"tid":1779064,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"12.11-13 1仔冰室One's cafe全日全單八折及不扣成本全數捐出","createTime":"2019-12-11T12:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T01:06:11.000Z","uid":343655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c014fc87ab06be570fce530165c42c82d60505a3","tid":1779064,"uid":343655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T12:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MPjSA0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMPjSA0d.jpg&h=82a63942&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n🎂12.12 1仔生日快樂🎁🎈🎊<br />\n藉住呢個咁開心既日子，1仔決定！要做返D有意義既事，你哋一定會支持1仔既✌️<br />\n<br />\n12月 11-13 日 ，為多謝及回饋各位街坊&amp;粉絲既支持！全日全單八折，歡迎堂食及外賣🎊🎉你卑幾錢1仔，1仔就捐幾錢😊活動完結後，將不扣成本捐出三天營業額。 款項捐出後會公開收據到1仔冰室Facebook Page 及IG.<br />\n<br />\n12月12日12點 1仔有一個簡單而隆重既切餅儀式！同時我地仲邀請咗1仔既好朋友&mdash;紅土家一齊慶祝🎉大家到時見啦✌️<br />\n<br />\n***特別鳴謝紅土家提供及設計海報😊<br />\n**活動其間視乎人手狀況，或未能提供外送服務。敬請原諒<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－ <br />\n1仔冰室地址 : 香港九龍紅磡必嘉街92-112號 紅磡灣中心地下9C鋪 <br />\n營業時間 : 星期一至日 早上7時至晚上11時 <br />\n聯絡電話 : 3118 8111 <br />\n#1仔冰室 #OnesCafe #紅磡 #黃埔 #冰室 #🇭🇰<br />\n#香港加油 #我愛香港 #紅土家 #星火 #612 #守護孩子 #捍衛民主 #捍衛香港 #光復香港<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Onescafehk/posts/559064984659168\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FOnescafehk%2Fposts%2F559064984659168&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnAItKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=86c26537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Onescafehk/posts/559064984659168</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z6gd4V5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz6gd4V5.png&h=a65dc070&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a53e041d37b1ade37a604b208da4ff029c4b8dd1","tid":1779064,"uid":343655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T12:14:07.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a2edac092552d7e04227d59388e49011429347","tid":1779064,"uid":56432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime